s="notion-text notion-block-378f952dff7d4d799a353942fa204eb7">我们已经制作了可以在 SpacemiT K1 开发板上直接运行的预编译 Fedora 镜像文件，您可点击以下链接选择您所需要的镜像:</div><ul class="notion-list notion-list-disc notion-block-fb94442c6d03499fb4bd3e76d7899917"><li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="notion-link" href="https://mirror.iscas.ac.cn/fedora-riscv/dl/SpacemiT/K1_M1/images/latest/k1-fedora-minimal.img.zst">Fedora 41 (Minimal)</a></li></ul><ul class="notion-list notion-list-disc notion-block-1e1076861f694e9ba37499f4c2fceda9"><li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="notion-link" href="https://mirror.iscas.ac.cn/fedora-riscv/dl/SpacemiT/K1_M1/images/latest/k1-fedora-multi-desktops.img.zst">Fedora 41 (Multi Desktop)</a></li></ul><h3 class="notion-h notion-h2 notion-h-indent-1 notion-block-637aa972a54a47fea29815238ff7e662" data-id="637aa972a54a47fea29815238ff7e662"><span><div id="637aa972a54a47fea29815238ff7e662" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#637aa972a54a47fea29815238ff7e662" title="解压镜像文件"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">解压镜像文件</span></span></h3><div class="notion-text notion-block-29d97c13a97142059d999ec53d612a51">下载上述任一镜像文件后，在镜像所在目录输入以下命令 (此处我们假设您下载的是 Fedora 41 Minimal)</div><h3 class="notion-h notion-h2 notion-h-indent-1 notion-block-d9b0156dd76842cd9c7afd90ec182880" data-id="d9b0156dd76842cd9c7afd90ec182880"><span><div id="d9b0156dd76842cd9c7afd90ec182880" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#d9b0156dd76842cd9c7afd90ec182880" title="写入TF卡"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">写入TF卡</span></span></h3><div class="notion-text notion-block-73c243c847194afa92d1d6251ce85f62">在进行烧写任务之前，我们强烈建议您使用 <code class="notion-inline-code">wipefs</code> 清理备份的GPT分区表，以免出现内核无法访问或挂载rootfs的问题。</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-d5183698fe4b40ea91790b2890591478">在执行下列命令前，请务必检查并正确修改以下与sdX相关的命令，使其正确指向您的 TF 卡</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-558765ca7cee4c3fbc980ab102b00851">您可以通过以下两种方式写入。</div><h4 class="notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-2 notion-block-a21911e20b414489a58f03faa653e6d3" data-id="a21911e20b414489a58f03faa653e6d3"><span><div id="a21911e20b414489a58f03faa653e6d3" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#a21911e20b414489a58f03faa653e6d3" title="方法一：使用dd命令写入"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">方法一：使用dd命令写入</span></span></h4><h4 class="notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-2 notion-block-f7cc7193c03148a5afad2e05f1a1034a" data-id="f7cc7193c03148a5afad2e05f1a1034a"><span><div id="f7cc7193c03148a5afad2e05f1a1034a" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#f7cc7193c03148a5afad2e05f1a1034a" title="方法二：使用 balenaEtcher 写入"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">方法二：使用 balenaEtcher 写入</span></span></h4><div class="notion-text notion-block-6c7b179d3dbc4ca4b2c6a9b1ce2c6c41">选择您下载好的镜像，并选择您需要烧录的 TF 卡，点击 Flash ，稍等片刻，等待镜像烧录完成。</div><figure class="notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-5604f1cd420d4568abc35bec98426d58"><div style="position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fprod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2F7bdf65e9-0afc-4b36-ac7c-3bbb5bc2636f%2Fa28654bb-a1a0-4cd4-81c5-a017347fd27e%2FUntitled.png?table=block&amp;id=5604f1cd-420d-4568-abc3-5bec98426d58&amp;t=5604f1cd-420d-4568-abc3-5bec98426d58&amp;width=529&amp;cache=v2" alt="notion image" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></figure><h3 class="notion-h notion-h2 notion-h-indent-1 notion-block-a681b1fb8d1c414f98e9c44b4e459088" data-id="a681b1fb8d1c414f98e9c44b4e459088"><span><div id="a681b1fb8d1c414f98e9c44b4e459088" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#a681b1fb8d1c414f98e9c44b4e459088" title="启动系统"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">启动系统</span></span></h3><div class="notion-text notion-block-f67dd15ade12427193b3672e94b2011a">接入 DC 电源或 Type-C 来供电，并连接 HDMI 线。如操作正确无误，您将会在显示器上看到类似以下的滚动输出</div><figure class="notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-408126945ded46d69b4ea5ea6eb1b8fa"><div style="position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fprod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2F7bdf65e9-0afc-4b36-ac7c-3bbb5bc2636f%2F61cdfc38-cf2d-4b2d-a14f-1bc161263e6a%2FUntitled.png?table=block&amp;id=40812694-5ded-46d6-9b4e-a5ea6eb1b8fa&amp;t=40812694-5ded-46d6-9b4e-a5ea6eb1b8fa&amp;width=2484&amp;cache=v2" alt="notion image" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></figure><h3 class="notion-h notion-h2 notion-h-indent-1 notion-block-c462ae6d36c040148e04b583c9198592" data-id="c462ae6d36c040148e04b583c9198592"><span><div id="c462ae6d36c040148e04b583c9198592" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#c462ae6d36c040148e04b583c9198592" title="连接串口"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">连接串口</span></span></h3><div class="notion-text notion-block-2c3e49b8133c41c08e7dc73024d571c3">在进行串口连接前，请务必检查您所使用的杜邦线每根跳线的功能，并仔细检查官方提供的 GPIO Pin 分布文档！错误的接入将有可能烧毁您的开发板！</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-0fa0268c93e24435ad45f7b146661022">接入串口连接线后，您可以使用 screen 或 minicom 连接到串口， K1 系列开发板的波特率默认为 115200。</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-7736fc0c58fd41ed929278abb7400f2b">Linux 设备路径： <code class="notion-inline-code">/dev/ttyUSBX</code></div><div class="notion-text notion-block-77343718de4a41f0b8db2391e7111e64">macOS 设备路径： <code class="notion-inline-code">/dev/tty.usbserial-XXXX</code></div><div class="notion-text notion-block-84972dbd78114065807f2bbab4deaaee">Windows 设备路径： <code class="notion-inline-code">(COMX)</code></div><h4 class="notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-2 notion-block-37f2220f30b2425c95f65bd58d63eb32" data-id="37f2220f30b2425c95f65bd58d63eb32"><span><div id="37f2220f30b2425c95f65bd58d63eb32" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#37f2220f30b2425c95f65bd58d63eb32" title="使用 screen 连接"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">使用 screen 连接</span></span></h4><div class="notion-text notion-block-ee463aee4d58405c92c4021be3d1ec00">您可在 Linux / macOS 设备上，使用 screen [设备路径] [波特率] 连接到开发板，以下为一个命令示例：</div><h4 class="notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-2 notion-block-e6d9ad4d635d4d5fa9e7ae820c0c195a" data-id="e6d9ad4d635d4d5fa9e7ae820c0c195a"><span><div id="e6d9ad4d635d4d5fa9e7ae820c0c195a" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#e6d9ad4d635d4d5fa9e7ae820c0c195a" title="使用 minicom 连接"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">使用 minicom 连接</span></span></h4><div class="notion-text notion-block-f8348553066a4d668b252c799b6ca9e8">您可在 Linux / macOS 设备上，使用 minicom 连接到设备。</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-43207f7d85f848d487307c00bfe2d1a0">在终端键入 <code class="notion-inline-code">minicom -s</code> ，跳转到 Serial port setup 选项卡，修改 Serial Device 和 Bps/Par/Bits ，将呈现类似以下</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-e7c5f238c0964136b6cf5ad8cef2d18d">配置完成后，选择 Save setup as dfl。</div><h4 class="notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-2 notion-block-74b6e2ba7bc74243a5f37ad27efec0d1" data-id="74b6e2ba7bc74243a5f37ad27efec0d1"><span><div id="74b6e2ba7bc74243a5f37ad27efec0d1" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#74b6e2ba7bc74243a5f37ad27efec0d1" title="使用支持串口连接的终端软件"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">使用支持串口连接的终端软件</span></span></h4><div class="notion-text notion-block-31dcc30646fc4c2b8f939d6927c535b4">您可在 Windows 设备上，使用支持串口连接的终端软件（如：Putty、XShell、MobaXTerm等），选择正确的设备，填入波特率为 <code class="notion-inline-code">115200</code> 进行连接。</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-2c83487f37754d5586891a7042226ed5">当您在控制台中可以看到类似如下输出时，表明串口已成功通信，您可耐心等待系统启动完成。</div><h3 class="notion-h notion-h2 notion-h-indent-1 notion-block-4356f5cfe5eb42769d1d7589195ae7ad" data-id="4356f5cfe5eb42769d1d7589195ae7ad"><span><div id="4356f5cfe5eb42769d1d7589195ae7ad" class="notion-header-anchor"></div><a class="notion-hash-link" href="#4356f5cfe5eb42769d1d7589195ae7ad" title="登录到服务器"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a><span class="notion-h-title">登录到服务器</span></span></h3><div class="notion-text notion-block-517cda3190314067b4fa6fdcbd713c78">系统完全启动后，您会看到以下内容</div><div class="notion-text notion-block-40052f6b1e1f45acbd778983c653f91b">默认的账户密码为 root / riscv 。</div></main></div>